@node Main "Cubuc - Documentation"

                               'Cubuc' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  "Cubuc" is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which you have to rotate and
line up cubic shapes of 4 different colours, so at least 4 of them
line up in the same direction. The more there are cubes that are
lined up, the more points you get. If all lined up cubes are of the
same colour, you get much more points. Every time you rotate a cube
and it does not create an aligment of at least 4 cubes lined up in
the same direction, one more cube will appear on the game board.

  Have fun!

